1
00:01:42,920 --> 00:01:43,719
Not bad

2
00:02:03,760 --> 00:02:05,200
What is this?

3
00:02:06,280 --> 00:02:07,519
It can actually erode me in return?

4
00:02:08,240 --> 00:02:08,800
This is...

5
00:02:09,919 --> 00:02:10,960
Such familiar black energy.

6
00:02:21,080 --> 00:02:22,919
This black energy is Vile Qi.

7
00:02:22,919 --> 00:02:24,240
It corrodes bones and pierces meridians.

8
00:02:24,240 --> 00:02:26,840
And ordinary people cannot see it.

9
00:02:26,840 --> 00:02:28,680
Only Violet Qi can subdue it.

10
00:02:28,680 --> 00:02:30,240
Shatter the evil curse.

11
00:02:30,240 --> 00:02:31,840
Guard the soul, protect the essence.

12
00:02:42,919 --> 00:02:44,319
One good deed a day.

13
00:02:44,319 --> 00:02:47,520
Mister, you're lucky you ran into me today.

14
00:02:56,800 --> 00:02:58,800
I'll take this as my consultation fee.

15
00:02:59,599 --> 00:03:00,400
No need to thank me.

16
00:03:07,560 --> 00:03:08,520
You're just here to fill a spot.

17
00:03:08,520 --> 00:03:09,560
Why are you still dawdling?

18
00:03:14,240 --> 00:03:15,919
Hurry up, put on the costume and mask.

19
00:03:16,520 --> 00:03:17,960
Even Medicine Holder Li has entered the contest.

20
00:03:18,520 --> 00:03:20,639
The prize is definitely out of your reach this time.

21
00:03:20,639 --> 00:03:21,680
It's the taking part that counts, right?

22
00:03:21,680 --> 00:03:23,240
Wait for me to change, I'll be right there.

23
00:03:28,439 --> 00:03:32,199
Medicine Master Lu.

24
00:03:32,199 --> 00:03:32,800
What is it?

25
00:03:32,800 --> 00:03:33,439
Medicine Master Lu.

26
00:03:33,439 --> 00:03:35,240
Panicking like that, you shame the Lu family.

27
00:03:35,240 --> 00:03:36,360
Medicine Master Lu, it's bad!

28
00:03:37,080 --> 00:03:37,840
What happened?

29
00:03:37,840 --> 00:03:38,639
Well...

30
00:03:38,639 --> 00:03:40,080
That contestant, Number Zero...

31
00:03:40,080 --> 00:03:40,800
For some reason...

32
00:03:40,800 --> 00:03:41,800
he's gone on stage.

33
00:03:43,360 --> 00:03:45,000
What?

34
00:03:45,000 --> 00:03:46,039
I don't know why either.

35
00:03:51,240 --> 00:03:54,199
If Number Zero takes the Art of the Tranquil Sea and Mind...

36
00:03:54,199 --> 00:03:54,879
you know the consequences.

37
00:03:54,879 --> 00:03:56,080
I know.

38
00:03:56,080 --> 00:03:57,080
I know the consequences.

39
00:03:57,800 --> 00:03:59,159
I'll definitely figure something out.

40
00:03:59,159 --> 00:04:01,159
I won't even let him pass the first round.

41
00:04:02,080 --> 00:04:02,800
Then hurry and go!

42
00:04:14,280 --> 00:04:15,919
This year is really different.

43
00:04:15,919 --> 00:04:17,120
They actually invited Boss Ye to host.

44
00:04:17,959 --> 00:04:19,560
Welcome, everyone, to the Mystic Medicine Association.

45
00:04:19,560 --> 00:04:21,079
The triennial exchange tournament.

46
00:04:21,639 --> 00:04:23,439
This tournament is truly remarkable.

47
00:04:23,439 --> 00:04:25,319
We've invited four Medicine Masters

48
00:04:25,319 --> 00:04:26,959
to serve as judges for this tournament.

49
00:04:27,519 --> 00:04:29,399
Medicine Master Ye.

50
00:04:29,399 --> 00:04:31,800
Medicine Master Li.

51
00:04:32,160 --> 00:04:33,279
Medicine Master Ge.

52
00:04:41,600 --> 00:04:44,839
And the acting Medicine Master who joined ten years ago,

53
00:04:45,759 --> 00:04:46,560
Medicine Master Lu.

54
00:04:48,920 --> 00:04:51,920
Now, please welcome our contestants to the stage.

55
00:04:51,920 --> 00:04:55,079
First, the most popular in our Mystic Medicine Association,

56
00:04:55,079 --> 00:04:56,839
the most acclaimed representative of the Tech Faction.

57
00:04:59,879 --> 00:05:06,600
Tech Faction!

58
00:05:06,600 --> 00:05:08,199
The Tech Faction is so cool!

59
00:05:08,199 --> 00:05:09,680
Yeah, those glasses are so cool!

60
00:05:10,279 --> 00:05:11,720
The Mystic Medicine Association tournament has begun.

61
00:05:11,720 --> 00:05:12,600
Hurry, watch the livestream!

62
00:05:13,040 --> 00:05:14,959
So high-tech, so cool!

63
00:05:17,639 --> 00:05:19,519
What's that? I've never seen it.

64
00:05:20,920 --> 00:05:21,800
That...

65
00:05:21,800 --> 00:05:22,560
That's a Spirit Analyzer.

66
00:05:23,079 --> 00:05:25,319
I saw it on the Mystic Medicine Association's livestream.

67
00:05:25,319 --> 00:05:26,079
Truly impressive.

68
00:05:31,279 --> 00:05:33,319
Next, please welcome our Mystic Medicine Association's

69
00:05:33,319 --> 00:05:34,920
inheritor of the Traditionalist Faction.

70
00:05:35,240 --> 00:05:36,120
Traditionalist Faction representative!

71
00:05:49,680 --> 00:05:52,319
The Traditionalist Faction has lost three in a row.

72
00:05:52,319 --> 00:05:53,360
How dare they still show their faces?

73
00:05:53,360 --> 00:05:55,040
And they're even wearing masks.

74
00:05:55,040 --> 00:05:56,680
Maybe they couldn't find anyone and brought in an outsider?

75
00:05:58,000 --> 00:05:58,800
Who knows.

76
00:05:59,160 --> 00:06:02,160
Of course, this year's prize is exceptional.

77
00:06:02,160 --> 00:06:04,079
It's the Yang family's heirloom technique,

78
00:06:04,079 --> 00:06:05,560
the Art of the Tranquil Sea and Mind.

79
00:06:07,480 --> 00:06:10,639
Is that the one for calming the mind?

80
00:06:10,639 --> 00:06:11,800
The Art of the Tranquil Sea and Mind?

81
00:06:11,800 --> 00:06:12,959
I've heard of that one.

82
00:06:12,959 --> 00:06:15,199
It's far more than just calming the mind.

83
00:06:15,199 --> 00:06:16,480
Legend says this technique

84
00:06:16,480 --> 00:06:18,240
can unify the five organs in an instant,

85
00:06:18,240 --> 00:06:20,519
and instantly suppress qi deviation.

86
00:06:20,519 --> 00:06:21,959
But ever since the Yang family fell,

87
00:06:21,959 --> 00:06:23,800
no one has witnessed its glory.

88
00:06:26,319 --> 00:06:28,079
Hey.

89
00:06:28,079 --> 00:06:29,319
Everyone.

90
00:06:29,319 --> 00:06:31,399
The Art of the Tranquil Sea and Mind

91
00:06:31,399 --> 00:06:33,920
is a thousand-year treasure of the Mystic Medicine Association.

92
00:06:35,199 --> 00:06:39,160
Medicine Master Ye has kept it on the Yang family's behalf.

93
00:06:39,160 --> 00:06:41,240
It is truly priceless.

94
00:06:41,240 --> 00:06:43,720
Even I have never laid eyes on it.

95
00:06:46,879 --> 00:06:48,079
Young ones,

96
00:06:49,120 --> 00:06:50,279
for your sake,

97
00:06:50,279 --> 00:06:54,560
we Medicine Masters pleaded long and hard

98
00:06:54,560 --> 00:06:59,319
before Master Ye agreed to offer it as this tournament's prize.

99
00:07:02,000 --> 00:07:03,600
To today's contestants:

100
00:07:03,600 --> 00:07:07,639
may you bear the weight of this sacred art

101
00:07:07,639 --> 00:07:10,480
without tarnishing the Association's honor,

102
00:07:11,199 --> 00:07:12,879
or defiling the Yang family's legacy.

103
00:07:26,279 --> 00:07:28,720
Round One: Break the Poison, Identify the Source.

104
00:07:28,720 --> 00:07:29,800
The pill before each of you

105
00:07:29,800 --> 00:07:33,399
is one of the deadliest toxins in the Mystic Medicine Association's archives.

106
00:07:33,399 --> 00:07:35,839
Its components are complex, its base shifting.

107
00:07:35,839 --> 00:07:39,040
You must analyze its properties within the time limit,

108
00:07:39,040 --> 00:07:40,879
and from the various herbs behind you,

109
00:07:40,879 --> 00:07:42,199
select the correct ingredients,

110
00:07:42,199 --> 00:07:43,839
and seal them in the box.

111
00:07:44,879 --> 00:07:46,839
One wrong herb means failure.

112
00:07:46,839 --> 00:07:49,000
Only perfect answers advance to the next round.

113
00:07:57,560 --> 00:07:59,279
Contestants, prepare yourselves.

114
00:07:59,279 --> 00:08:00,079
Let the competition begin!

115
00:08:24,720 --> 00:08:25,480
What's he even doing?

116
00:08:27,399 --> 00:08:29,000
Is he here for the competition?

117
00:08:29,000 --> 00:08:30,279
What is all this stuff?

118
00:08:36,279 --> 00:08:38,000
Bro, that's pretty high-tech.

119
00:08:38,000 --> 00:08:39,120
Sweeping for mines?

120
00:08:39,120 --> 00:08:40,200
Scan mine too, will ya?

121
00:08:40,200 --> 00:08:41,639
Get lost.

122
00:08:41,639 --> 00:08:43,480
Country bumpkin, don't ruin my match.

123
00:08:46,080 --> 00:08:47,279
The exchange contest is really lively.

124
00:08:47,279 --> 00:08:48,600
Even secret agents are competing.

125
00:08:48,600 --> 00:08:49,559
So now the Traditionalist Faction

126
00:08:49,559 --> 00:08:51,120
has stooped to copying answers?

127
00:08:51,840 --> 00:08:52,279
No.

128
00:08:52,279 --> 00:08:53,159
You've got it wrong.

129
00:08:53,159 --> 00:08:53,919
I was just curious.

130
00:08:53,919 --> 00:08:54,799
Just having a look.

131
00:09:03,759 --> 00:09:05,759
What's that Traditionalist guy up to?

132
00:09:05,759 --> 00:09:06,759
Just wandering around.

133
00:09:06,759 --> 00:09:07,960
Did he give up on the match?

134
00:09:07,960 --> 00:09:10,759
Looks like a country bumpkin's first time in the city.

135
00:09:10,759 --> 00:09:12,919
Never seen so much high-tech gear.

136
00:09:12,919 --> 00:09:13,799
Treating the contest like a tour.

137
00:09:14,320 --> 00:09:16,840
Bro, that gadget's like a cheat code.

138
00:09:16,840 --> 00:09:18,720
Get lost, don't ruin my match.

139
00:09:19,559 --> 00:09:20,799
What's so impressive about it?

140
00:09:22,159 --> 00:09:23,919
You country bumpkin, are you out of your mind?

141
00:09:23,919 --> 00:09:26,480
How dare you break my Spirit Analyzer with your filthy hands!

142
00:09:26,480 --> 00:09:28,879
Clearly your gadget's just poor quality.

143
00:09:30,120 --> 00:09:32,399
Doesn't your faction identify herbs by smell?

144
00:09:32,399 --> 00:09:35,399
So when it fails, you start messing with us?

145
00:09:35,399 --> 00:09:36,960
If you can identify herbs by smell,

146
00:09:36,960 --> 00:09:38,159
identifying a poison pill should be easy.

147
00:09:38,720 --> 00:09:39,679
Fine.

148
00:09:39,679 --> 00:09:40,679
Then go ahead, give it a sniff.

149
00:09:40,679 --> 00:09:41,879
I will, then.

150
00:09:48,200 --> 00:09:52,240
Yinluo flower, crimson sand seed, badger gall, ethereal vine.

151
00:09:52,240 --> 00:09:53,039
Heart-Eroding Nightmare Poison.

152
00:09:54,399 --> 00:09:55,679
Whoa.

153
00:09:55,679 --> 00:09:56,720
My nose is that good?

154
00:09:57,360 --> 00:10:00,120
Don't blame me for your inferior hardware.

155
00:10:01,120 --> 00:10:01,799
You...

156
00:10:04,480 --> 00:10:05,120
Sorry.

157
00:10:05,120 --> 00:10:05,879
I didn't mean to.

158
00:10:05,879 --> 00:10:06,440
I had no idea

159
00:10:06,440 --> 00:10:07,519
your nerves were so fragile.

160
00:10:09,799 --> 00:10:10,399
What are you doing?

161
00:10:10,399 --> 00:10:10,960
Get down!

162
00:10:10,960 --> 00:10:14,759
Get off!

163
00:10:14,759 --> 00:10:17,360
Ten minutes remaining.

164
00:10:17,360 --> 00:10:19,639
Get off!

165
00:10:20,960 --> 00:10:21,919
You...

166
00:10:23,720 --> 00:10:25,279
You just wait!

167
00:10:38,039 --> 00:10:40,320
Five minutes remaining.

168
00:10:49,399 --> 00:10:51,639
Three minutes remaining.

169
00:10:59,519 --> 00:11:02,279
One minute remaining.

170
00:11:11,000 --> 00:11:12,279
Time's up.

171
00:11:12,279 --> 00:11:14,879
Judges, please reveal each contestant's medicine box.

172
00:11:16,559 --> 00:11:17,360
Eliminated.

173
00:11:19,000 --> 00:11:19,639
Passed.

174
00:11:22,240 --> 00:11:23,039
Eliminated.

175
00:11:24,679 --> 00:11:25,440
Passed.

176
00:11:30,840 --> 00:11:33,639
Judges, please reveal Contestant No. 1's box.

177
00:11:33,639 --> 00:11:35,200
No need to even check Medicine Holder Li's.

178
00:11:35,200 --> 00:11:36,559
It's definitely flawless.

179
00:11:41,159 --> 00:11:43,600
Contestant No. 1 passes with all correct.

180
00:11:43,600 --> 00:11:44,600
Medicine Holder Li's doesn't need checking, definitely flawless.

181
00:11:44,600 --> 00:11:46,559
Who's more accurate than Medicine Holder Li at identifying herbs?

182
00:11:46,559 --> 00:11:47,799
Medicine Holder Li truly is the pride of the Mystic Medicine Association.

183
00:11:47,799 --> 00:11:48,720
Watch closely,

184
00:11:48,720 --> 00:11:49,879
country bumpkin.

185
00:11:50,559 --> 00:11:52,360
This is what real skill looks like.

186
00:11:52,360 --> 00:11:55,559
Let me show you what a real...

187
00:12:01,440 --> 00:12:02,279
A giant bug?!

188
00:12:02,919 --> 00:12:03,720
I'm dying laughing.

189
00:12:03,720 --> 00:12:04,919
Is No. 0 here for comedy?

190
00:12:04,919 --> 00:12:06,639
Where did that bug come from?

191
00:12:06,639 --> 00:12:08,200
Don't tell me it's No. 0's pet.

192
00:12:29,960 --> 00:12:32,039
So what if you guessed the pill right?

193
00:12:32,039 --> 00:12:34,639
The test is finding the right antidote herbs.

194
00:12:34,639 --> 00:12:36,039
The herbs are all gone.

195
00:12:36,039 --> 00:12:37,360
How are you going to win?

196
00:12:37,360 --> 00:12:38,559
Medicine Master Ye.

197
00:12:38,559 --> 00:12:40,600
This performance art from your Traditionalist Faction

198
00:12:40,600 --> 00:12:41,919
is truly impressive.

199
00:12:41,919 --> 00:12:44,399
But it seems you'll go home empty-handed again.

200
00:12:45,600 --> 00:12:47,440
How embarrassing.

201
00:12:50,320 --> 00:12:51,080
Please wait, everyone.

202
00:12:53,720 --> 00:12:55,960
The real showstopper is still to come.

203
00:12:59,600 --> 00:13:00,440
Brother Bug.

204
00:13:00,919 --> 00:13:02,639
Did you eat up all my herbs?

205
00:13:03,440 --> 00:13:05,320
Spit them back out, now.

206
00:13:05,879 --> 00:13:07,039
Has Number Zero lost his mind?

207
00:13:07,399 --> 00:13:08,840
He's actually talking to a bug.

208
00:13:08,840 --> 00:13:10,279
He just can't win,

209
00:13:10,279 --> 00:13:11,159
so now he's pulling stunts.

210
00:13:14,360 --> 00:13:15,519
So this is your big show?

211
00:13:18,960 --> 00:13:20,159
What's the rush?

212
00:13:30,919 --> 00:13:34,440
Severed grass shall not die; qi flows through its root.

213
00:13:34,440 --> 00:13:38,039
Breath of Primordial, defy heaven and restore life.

214
00:13:43,240 --> 00:13:44,240
Just as I thought, my Violet Qi

215
00:13:44,240 --> 00:13:46,000
can regrow herbs from mere scraps.

216
00:13:48,799 --> 00:13:50,159
Amazing, Number Zero!

217
00:13:50,159 --> 00:13:52,039
Didn't expect the Traditionalist Faction to have such skill.

218
00:13:52,039 --> 00:13:53,600
You cheated!

219
00:13:54,960 --> 00:13:55,559
Incredible!

220
00:13:57,000 --> 00:13:57,600
What's going on?

221
00:13:58,840 --> 00:13:59,759
I have no idea either.

222
00:14:00,840 --> 00:14:02,240
You're too kind, everyone.

223
00:14:02,240 --> 00:14:03,519
I just know a few little magic tricks,

224
00:14:03,519 --> 00:14:04,919
just to spice things up for you all.

225
00:14:08,720 --> 00:14:09,919
Impressive.

226
00:14:09,919 --> 00:14:10,759
Truly impressive.

227
00:14:10,759 --> 00:14:13,440
Our final advancing contestant has emerged.

228
00:14:13,440 --> 00:14:15,759
Number Zero from the Traditionalist Faction.

229
00:14:15,759 --> 00:14:16,440
Congratulations on advancing.

230
00:14:17,159 --> 00:14:18,320
Thank you.

231
00:14:19,279 --> 00:14:20,279
What a clown.

232
00:14:27,360 --> 00:14:29,679
The next round is live diagnosis.

233
00:14:29,679 --> 00:14:31,200
Please take a brief rest, contestants.

234
00:14:32,000 --> 00:14:33,720
See you at the next round, then.

235
00:14:35,919 --> 00:14:39,279
Next time, you won't be so lucky.

236
00:14:47,200 --> 00:14:48,159
Xiao Qiu.

237
00:14:48,159 --> 00:14:49,039
Who is that Number Zero?

238
00:14:50,919 --> 00:14:54,320
Boss Ye, the data says Vice Medicine Master Cheng Qi.

239
00:14:55,399 --> 00:14:56,559
He absolutely can't be Uncle Cheng.

240
00:15:02,399 --> 00:15:04,120
I'll just play a bomb.

241
00:15:05,039 --> 00:15:05,919
Take that!

242
00:15:07,559 --> 00:15:08,519
Bomb!

243
00:15:08,519 --> 00:15:09,600
Wait, what...

244
00:15:09,600 --> 00:15:10,639
Who is it?

245
00:15:13,720 --> 00:15:14,559
Brother-in-law.

246
00:15:14,559 --> 00:15:16,000
Calm down.

247
00:15:16,480 --> 00:15:17,519
Don't be angry.

248
00:15:17,519 --> 00:15:18,759
Life is just like a play, you know.

249
00:15:20,399 --> 00:15:21,159
Don't be mad.

250
00:15:26,600 --> 00:15:27,360
Come on, brother-in-law.

251
00:15:39,080 --> 00:15:41,360
Who exactly is this Number Zero?

252
00:15:42,120 --> 00:15:43,240
Brother-in-law, don't be angry.

253
00:15:43,240 --> 00:15:43,960
Close the door.

254
00:15:43,960 --> 00:15:44,559
Yes.

255
00:15:44,559 --> 00:15:46,279
He was just lucky in round one.

256
00:15:46,720 --> 00:15:48,080
The poison in round two

257
00:15:48,080 --> 00:15:50,200
is custom-made by our Hequan Pharmaceutical.

258
00:15:51,480 --> 00:15:53,120
No matter how skilled he is,

259
00:15:54,120 --> 00:15:55,120
he'll be crawling out on his knees.

260
00:15:58,360 --> 00:15:59,679
Calm down.

261
00:15:59,679 --> 00:16:00,720
It's fine.

262
00:16:02,039 --> 00:16:02,639
Get the hell out!

263
00:16:08,039 --> 00:16:08,840
Son-in-law.

264
00:16:10,039 --> 00:16:12,720
You couldn't get the Primordial Violet Qi Art,

265
00:16:12,720 --> 00:16:14,440
leaving my Xiang unable to recover.

266
00:16:15,519 --> 00:16:17,720
If you fail to obtain the Art of the Tranquil Sea and Mind,

267
00:16:18,399 --> 00:16:20,080
you useless lot can get the hell out of the Mystic Medicine Association!

268
00:16:20,559 --> 00:16:21,600
In-law.

269
00:16:21,600 --> 00:16:22,320
Don't worry.

270
00:16:23,840 --> 00:16:24,840
Yes.

271
00:16:25,840 --> 00:16:27,480
Come, have some tea.

272
00:16:34,320 --> 00:16:36,120
Even if someone else takes it,

273
00:16:36,120 --> 00:16:37,759
the Art of the Tranquil Sea and Mind

274
00:16:37,759 --> 00:16:40,559
will only matter if they live to use it.

275
00:16:48,600 --> 00:16:49,879
Round two:

276
00:16:49,879 --> 00:16:51,360
live diagnosis.

277
00:16:51,360 --> 00:16:52,919
This round will test the contestants'

278
00:16:52,919 --> 00:16:54,799
observation, listening, inquiry, and palpation,

279
00:16:54,799 --> 00:16:56,559
pushing their fundamentals to the absolute limit.

280
00:16:56,559 --> 00:16:57,759
Facing real patients,

281
00:16:57,759 --> 00:16:59,200
with a time limit of ten minutes,

282
00:16:59,200 --> 00:17:00,919
contestants must rely solely on visual observation,

283
00:17:00,919 --> 00:17:02,960
verbal inquiry, and pulse reading

284
00:17:02,960 --> 00:17:04,880
to write a complete treatment plan.

285
00:17:04,880 --> 00:17:07,240
Only one contestant's plan will be chosen

286
00:17:07,240 --> 00:17:08,440
for live medication testing.

287
00:17:12,400 --> 00:17:13,279
The competition begins!

288
00:17:15,720 --> 00:17:16,880
This poison is just too complex.

289
00:17:16,880 --> 00:17:17,480
I really can't cure it.

290
00:17:17,480 --> 00:17:18,279
I withdraw.

291
00:17:21,920 --> 00:17:23,519
I can't even identify the source of the poison.

292
00:17:23,519 --> 00:17:24,759
It's simply unsolvable!

293
00:17:25,960 --> 00:17:26,759
I withdraw.

294
00:17:27,880 --> 00:17:28,559
What's wrong?

295
00:17:29,519 --> 00:17:30,599
Technology failing you?

296
00:17:30,960 --> 00:17:32,599
Can't even write a prescription?

297
00:17:37,720 --> 00:17:39,599
Now we welcome the final contestant.

298
00:17:41,839 --> 00:17:44,759
You're up, country bumpkin.

299
00:18:08,880 --> 00:18:09,960
Is this a serious exam?

300
00:18:20,799 --> 00:18:21,720
It's actually her.

301
00:18:22,480 --> 00:18:23,839
You've been so hard to find.
